<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 3. Habitus (dorsal) II a O. gracilis Westwood (imaged specimen: OGr 01; ovipositor not visible in full length) b O. heikewernerae sp. n. (OHe 01, holotype) c O. hoggarensis Hedqvist (OHo 02, paratype) d O. leibnizi sp. n. (OLe 01, holotype) e O. longicollis (Cameron) (OLo 01) f O. madegassa Boucek (OMad 01, holotype). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 12. Mesosoma (dorsal) II a O. gracilis Westwood (imaged specimen: OGr 01) b O. heikewernerae sp. n. (OHe 01, holotype) c O. hoggarensis Hedqvist (OHo 02, paratype) d O. leibnizi sp. n. (OLe 01, holotype) e O. longicollis (Cameron) (OLo 01) f O. madegassa Boucek (OMad 01, holotype). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 9. Head (lateral) II a O. gracilis Westwood (imaged specimen: OGr 01) b O. heikewernerae sp. n. (OHe 01, holotype) c O. hoggarensis Hedqvist (OHo 02, paratype) d O. leibnizi sp. n. (OLe 03, paratype) e O. longicollis (Cameron) (OLo 01) f O. madegassa Boucek (OMad 01, holotype). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 15. Mesoscutellum and propodeum (dorsal) II a O. gracilis Westwood (imaged specimen: OGr 01) b O. heikewernerae sp. n. (OHe 01, holotype) c O. hoggarensis Hedqvist (OHo 02, paratype) d O. leibnizi sp. n. (OLe 03, paratype) e O. longicollis (Cameron) (OLo 01) f O. madegassa Boucek (OMad 01, holotype). Scale bars: 1 mm." , "Figure 6. Head (frontal) II a O. gracilis Westwood (imaged specimen: OGr 01) b O. heikewernerae sp. n. (OHe 01, holotype) c O. hoggarensis Hedqvist (OHo 02, paratype) d O. leibnizi sp. n. (OLe 03, paratype) e O. longicollis (Cameron) (OLo 01) f O. madegassa Boucek (OMad 01, holotype). Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199736" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199730" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199724" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199733" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/199727" .

